Replace this file with a real screenshot named demo.png.

How to capture:
  1. python model/train_pipeline_model.py
  2. uvicorn api.main:app --reload
  3. cd frontend && npm run dev
  4. Open http://localhost:5173
  5. Screenshot the full dashboard at 1440px width
  6. Save as docs/demo.png
  7. Update README.md line:
       > **Screenshot coming soon**
     to:
       ![Dashboard](docs/demo.png)
